data binding
            -sharing data inside the component



         1.  one way binding :- data sharing onlyb one direction


            ts- component
            html- view

            1.1 component to view:- ts file -> html file
              a) string interpolation -{{expression}}
              b) property binding -[attribute_name]="property"
            1.2  view to component:- html-> ts
              a) event binding-(event_name)="function_name()"
              b)event binding using  $event